overview: Manuel Deboxer is now in charge of our casting crew. He hasn't been in the business for a while so he's got some catching up to do. Gotta please Deboxer or else you're out! Ryan went to collect the rent even though David made arrangements with Peter to delay the payment. Ryan had something else in mind. The money was not the issue. He simply wanted to get fucked by the new tenant I hired muscles to help me move to my new place. While my friend, the young bodybuilder Brad, helped me carry heavy boxes, I couldn't stop noticing his biceps at work. I wanted to see a lot more.
title: Fantasy Stories: Volume 1
